title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Pulp Of Wood, Fibrous Matl. & Waste & Scrap
description: Imports Intra Eu - Pulp Of Wood, Fibrous Matl. & Waste & Scrap in the United Kingdom decreased to 39.36 GBP Million in September from 40.84 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Pulp Of Wood, Fibrous Matl. & W in the United Kingdom averaged 21.33 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 45.80 GBP Million in November of 2017 and a record low of 11.72 GBP Million in August of 2003. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Pulp of Wood, Fibrous Matl.
